AUDIO: 'Running one AI coding agent, it\'s easy. We do it all the time. Running five or 10 at once, it turns into a mess real quick. Tabs everywhere, tmux sessions you can\'t track, one agent stuck, another wrecking your branch, and you have no idea which is which. This is'

[00:13] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Agent of Empires, the mission control dashboard that lets you command all your AI agents from one screen. In the next 60 seconds, I\'ll show you why this is picking up traction. All right. Now, quick reset here. Um'

[00:30] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Agent of Empires is not another coding agent, okay? No. It doesn\'t replace Claude, Codex, or anything else. It just sits above them. It runs everything you\'re already using in your workflow.'

[00:42] [scene:talk]
